LIST ideas = done_theme, done_memor, done_feeli

LIST type_feeli = joy, sadness, tenderness

LIST type_memor = sunday, departure, encounter

LIST saw_ideas = yes, (no)

VAR saw_theme = no
VAR saw_memor = no
VAR saw_feeli = no


===park===
You walk {|back} into the park. The weather is nice, the wind blows through the trees. On the grass, people are playing a nice guitar tune. In the sky, a pair of birds is flying by. #loc[park] #hide[4]
    * [Look at the trees]
        The wind blowing in the tree reminds you to nature and brings up joyful memories about a lazy sunday you spent together.
            ** {saw_theme == no} [Think about nature] 
            
            ~ theme = "nature"
            {theme_ok()}
            #thm[nature]
            
            ** {saw_memor == no} [Remember the lazy sunday]
            
            ~ memor = "a lazy sunday"
            ~ type_memor = sunday
            {memor_ok()}
            #mem[sunday]
            
            ** {saw_feeli == no} [Experience joy]
            
            ~ feeli = "joy"
            ~ type_feeli = joy
            {feeli_ok()}
            #fel[joy]
            
            -- {get_back_from_park()} -> hub
            
    * [Listen to the tune]
        As you listen to the song the people are playing on the guitar, you feel culturally involved but the tune reminds you to a sad moment when you had to say goodbye.
            ** {saw_theme == no} [Enjoy the song]
            
            ~ theme = "culture"
            {theme_ok()}
            #thm[culture]
            
            ** {saw_memor == no} [Dive back into the memory]
            
            ~ memor = "a separation"
            ~ type_memor = departure
            {memor_ok()}
            #mem[departure]
            
            ** {saw_feeli == no} [Focus on the sadness]
            
            ~ feeli = "sadness"
            ~ type_feeli = sadness
            {feeli_ok()}
            #fel[sadness]
            
            -- {get_back_from_park()} -> hub
            
    * [Watch the birds fly]
        While you follow with your eyes the birds flapping to the sun, you think about when you first encounter during a trip and this memory brings back a tender feeling.
            ** {saw_theme == no} [Think about travel]
            
            ~ theme = "travel"
            {theme_ok()}
            #thm[travel]
            
            ** {saw_memor == no} [Remember your first encounter]
            
            ~ memor = "your first encounter"
            ~ type_memor = encounter
            {memor_ok()}
            #mem[encounter]
            
            ** {saw_feeli == no} [Enjoy the warmth of this feeling]
            
            ~ feeli = "tenderness"
            ~ type_feeli = tenderness
            {feeli_ok()}
            #fel[tenderness]
            
            -- {get_back_from_park()} -> hub
            
    + [Head back to the street]
    You're not inspired by this place and decide to go elsewhere. -> hub

