===museum===
The museum is {|still} very quiet. As you wander about, you can see some beautiful paintings and nice statues. Your eyes get caught by a visitor. #loc[museum] #hide[4]
    * [Gaze at the paintings]
        On one of the paintings you can see natural landscapes with some people stepping on a boat. It reminds you of when you had to take a train early and brings back all the tenderness of that time.
    
            ** {saw_theme == no} [Plunge into the beauty of the trees]
        
            ~ theme = "nature"
            {theme_ok()}
            #thm[nature]
        
            ** {saw_memor == no} [Remember the early departure]
        
